既悲哀。<br />\n<br />\n點拆？撚知咩。最大可能係有一日，有一樣微不足道或者突然到無人預計過會短時間發生既事，突然出現，令中共倒台/換人，可能係中美金融戰、中國內戰、出兵台灣反被滅、兵變換人、小熊突然死亡等等。<br />\n<br />\n而黎緊幾個月，應該都係示威、鎮壓無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b6277fb8f2e1772e0235424903ce94e57570d4","tid":1320891,"uid":55873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47dcd4b6a16c2dbc5834253f5ba84f04abeca204","tid":1320891,"uid":75407,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n依家成個連登都太high<br />\n希望出面既兄弟冷靜少少入黎睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5182b9d9447683c6e0fb7519541844e655315526","tid":1320891,"uid":242184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"咁重裝備 咁撚易死咩"},{"pid":"07fff78fe9e6407bb7d169ae342797fa638adb87","tid":1320891,"uid":75407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5182b9d9447683c6e0fb7519541844e655315526","tid":1320891,"uid":242184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"咁重裝備 咁撚易死咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3MhoRGf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3MhoRGf.gif&h=222717f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你話呢"},{"pid":"619296a4499db30989765baff101cb504d2085bf","tid":1320891,"uid":276198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdfc33a860f2020d854a77b36a10ab9bd809dd3c","tid":1320891,"uid":267437,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"原來係8964武器特登擺係街度等學生攞，cLs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"h